Code.NativeIaC:
```bicep
resource workspace 'Microsoft.Databricks/workspaces@2023-02-01' = {
  name: '<example_resource_name>'
  location: '<example_location>'
  sku: { name: 'premium' }
  properties: {
    managedResourceGroupId: '<example_resource_id>'
    parameters: {
      enableNoPublicIp: {
        value: true // Critical: prevents public IPs on cluster nodes
      }
    }
  }
}
```

Code.Terraform:
```hcl
resource "azurerm_databricks_workspace" "<example_resource_name>" {
  name                = "<example_resource_name>"
  location            = "<example_resource_id>"
  resource_group_name = "<example_resource_id>"
  sku                 = "premium"

  custom_parameters {
    no_public_ip = true  # Critical: no public IPs on cluster nodes
  }
}
```
